pt今時今日都有人信，唔怪得港豬成日畀人笑</blockquote><br />\n嗰班人多數都係商界，唔會真正愛國,但泛民唔同,泛民係真心愛國愛黨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打要分清大中華膠同奶共狗，大中華膠未必奶共但做得建制狗就一定奶共囉。"},{"pid":"82e9ef60acb3788cc01634cf0acf6d0ee6ac8b20","tid":277470,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:19:59.000Z","msg":"唔撚知邊個奶共傳媒幫班奶共狗改左個建制派來漂白，美化，但又一大班傻鳩跟。"},{"pid":"b011a1fc176c41d50df423b745e784b401fa8d74","tid":277470,"uid":35460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7951d4f30ad455ffdbe44dd40d65e823585051ca","tid":277470,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保皇黨囉 得未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保皇狗就保皇狗啦，黨乜鳩呀？"},{"pid":"e17b67ac6d6f50056a0b2a3a5af9052af8794f08","tid":277470,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T09:26:13.000Z","msg":"共狗就共狗,無其他選擇"},{"pid":"885e28b7f2f8bbffe11214de9a03f22ef8974397","tid":277470,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共狗就共狗,無其他選擇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見d飯民，本土重成日稱呼班共狗做建制派，真係無撚腦，果班奶共狗係敵人㴝，你重要美化班食屎狗？"},{"pid":"87a41d9ab5b04b23d25140a6b41dc34cea54dc2c","tid":277470,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdd73db16cac057d12babeb0c4f48c69bbf2bac","tid":277470,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建制同親共兩樣嘢嚟㗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有乜分別，兩者都是奶共，兩者都是共產黨d狗？<br />\n唔好扮複雜啦唔該。</blockquote><br />\n田大少、薯片、胡官呢啲都係建制<br />\n但同奶共兩個字大欖都扯唔埋<br />